</blockquote>
<p>I think I love you (in a completely non-creepy, non-cyber-stalker way).</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:64911459,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3399606&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;11311001&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;meddlingmonk&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c64911459" title="Link to this comment">#3.7</a> - Sat Apr 21, 2012 7:20 PM EDT</span></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c64877719"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:64877719,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;mego98125&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Mego98125&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://mego98125.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://mego98125.newsvine.com/">Mego98125</a></div></div><div id="commentText_64877719" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>You have no idea how angry this makes me.  The REPUBLICANS whine and snivel about the lack of educated people to fullfill the jobs in this country and then cut the access to education in this country.  Then they take money from the foreign corporations to up the number of H-1B visas and then piously wring their hands on immigration.  I HATE THEM.  Virginia Foxx is a moron who has zero credibility when she speaks.  Not only should we ELECT